name: It's a Trap! - D&D 5E Shaped theme
description: # It's A Trap! - 5th Edition (Shapedv2) theme_v3.0 updates:_* The trap theme has been made compatible with Its A Trap v3.0._v1.2 updates:_* This version only contains code refactoring. If there are any problems, revert to the previous version._v1.1 updates:_* The theme now supports the 'fx' basic JSON property made available in It's A Trap! v2.3.This is a D&D 5th edition trap theme for the It's A Trap! script, compatible withthe 5th Edition (Shapedv2) character sheet by Mlenser.To use this theme for the It's A Trap! script, enter '5E-Shaped' for the ```theme``` user option.
